{"tid":722393,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵好波","createTime":"2018-06-29T12:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T13:06:45.000Z","uid":8985,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34bc355cfc7ec367517d1f62c0ac096a4de55f8a","tid":722393,"uid":8985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:52:29.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕2018俄羅斯世足賽無疑是近期全球矚目的大事，由足球巨星「C朗」（Cristiano Ronaldo）領銜的葡萄牙國家隊順利挺進16強，正在美國訪問的葡萄牙總統德索薩（Marcelo Rebelo de Sousa），也趁機向美國總統特朗普推銷這位國家英雄，但特朗普突然問說，「他出來選總統會打敗你嗎？」讓德索薩一時不知該如何回答。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普27日在白宮橢圓辦公室與德索薩進行公開會面，過程中兩人不忘提及如火如荼進行的世足賽。德索薩說，「別忘了我們有全世界最好的足球員，他就是C朗，我相信你的兒子認識他」，特朗普附和，「確實，我的兒子對他非常了解。」<br />\n<br />\n德索薩說，「別忘了，如果你在世足冠軍戰期間訪問俄羅斯，葡萄牙仍會在那裡企圖贏得總冠軍」，特朗普則說，「你說得沒錯，他們表現得很好」，德索薩呼應，「對，他們表現得非常非常棒。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普問，「告訴我，他（C朗）有多棒？」德索薩回答，「我對他非常欽佩，他是全世界最好的球員」，特朗普追問，「<span style=\"color: red;\">那麼，C朗可能會競選總統並且擊敗你嗎？</span>」、「<span style=\"color: red;\">他不會贏對吧？</span>」德索薩聽到這個問題深吸一口氣，想了一下後才說，「我必須告訴你，葡萄牙和美國是不太一樣的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpn4Y5S5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpn4Y5S5.jpg&h=57f5dbaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙總統德索薩（左）大力向特朗普（右）讚賞C朗。（歐新社）"},{"pid":"6192b85a108eb5beb41c5c801558d25b3a02bd1b","tid":722393,"uid":3844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e752dda79c0eb9c254ebd0b315633400649a8833","tid":722393,"uid":38982,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6192b85a108eb5beb41c5c801558d25b3a02bd1b","tid":722393,"uid":3844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"侵侵都唔撚睇波你係咁煩鳩佢抵比串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b12cc4fe14d2d33d8980d8ee0dd6cce879d86c","tid":722393,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"Trump明顯對足球冇興趣先亂up一通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d605b74ef093632307ed03be68959ca129d986e","tid":722393,"uid":38982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b12cc4fe14d2d33d8980d8ee0dd6cce879d86c","tid":722393,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:00:58.000Z","msg":"Trump明顯對足球冇興趣先亂up一通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"同佢講摔角可能岩咁形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883fd0b92b26c11eefefa1f53d01aa2e0aca7195","tid":722393,"uid":49144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8759db69b3642481ce4257d0a25455d97870fc93","tid":722393,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T13:06:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">轉數好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"}]}